---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        I'm a full-stack software developer with 5 years of expertise in Spree Commerce and building scalable web applications.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-none space-y-1 text-base text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 text-lg">•</span>
          E-commerce Expert (5 years with Spree Commerce)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 text-lg">•</span>
          Backend Development (Ruby on Rails, Python, Django)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 text-lg">•</span>
          Frontend Development (React, JavaScript, HTML/CSS)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 text-lg">•</span>
          Database & Performance (PostgreSQL, Redis, Sidekiq)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 text-lg">•</span>
          Cloud & DevOps (AWS, Docker, Capistrano)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      I specialize in building and scaling e-commerce platforms, with deep expertise in Spree Commerce customization, payment integrations, and performance optimization.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      My experience includes implementing complex features like multi-vendor support, custom payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal, Razorpay), automated inventory management, and analytics integrations.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
